The paper discusses the combination of two popular reinforcement learning algorithms, neural evolution strategy (NES) and proximal policy optimization (PPO), to improve exploration. This topic falls under the broad category of machine learning and specifically, reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
